    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285180/extras/e059920cbaeb1f10d5c88e367dd8c07d.webp?t=1746985313\" width=586 height=44 /></span><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore an open world. <br></li><li>Platform to secret areas. <br></li><li>Solve puzzles. <br></li><li>Find optional bosses and collectibles. </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285180/extras/130653dccb8ea77015dbe0215e8b19b3.webp?t=1746985313\" width=586 height=44 /></span><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Form a team of monsters to fight for you.<br></li><li>Use strategy to beat larger groups of monsters that would overpower you otherwise. </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285180/extras/3226b75eceb246e8c70ddbc515f4bbc0.webp?t=1746985313\" width=586 height=44 /></span><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tame every monster that can appear in the game. <br></li><li>Some of them have unique traits and colors. </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285180/extras/95d2d92230c6696edecaba7c5395f707.webp?t=1746985313\" width=586 height=44 /></span><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Choose what your monster will evolve into with multiple choices at every stage. <br></li><li>Unlock rare evolutions previously unseen. </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285180/extras/2828951411dab69ad8feb1617902f206.webp?t=1746985313\" width=586 height=43 /></span><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pair monsters together to create a new life. <br></li><li>Merge unique traits together and create powerful offsprings. </li></ul>",
